  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this multi-center, prospective observational study is to determine the
      feasibility of a potential interventional study with fidaxomicin. The incidence and clinical
      aspects of Clostridium difficile infection (CDI) in neonates will be determined, and it will
      be assessed whether a subgroup can be identified where treatment with fidaxomicin therapy
      might improve outcome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
